'''Séu-thì-khìm''' (yu hêm-cho '''Vái-io-lìn'''<ref>[http://wiki.hakka.gov.tw/search-result.aspx Hak-kâ Ve-yèn-fi chhṳ̀ chhà-sûn kiet-kó]</ref>) he si-hièn ke [[kiûng-hièn ngo̍k-hi]], hien-thoi [[kón-hièn ngo̍k-thòn]] hièn-ngo̍k-chû thu chui chhùng-yeu ke [[ngo̍k-hi]], yit-pân chhai kón-hièn-ngo̍k chok-phín thu fi fûn-sṳ̀n [[thi-yit séu-thì-khìm]] lâu [[thi-ngi séu-thì-khìm]] lióng-ke sâng-phu. Chok-vì hien-thoi hièn-ngo̍k-hi tú chui khí fun-liòng ke ngo̍k-hi, séu-thì-khìm chú-yeu ke thi̍t-tiám chhai-yî khì fî-fông ke sâng-yîm, kô-thu ke yên-cheu kî-kháu lâu fûng-fu, kóng-fàm ke péu-hien-li̍t. Yu fûn hêm-cho ngo̍k-hi tú ke ńg-vòng<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.taiwanfun.com/central/taichung/articles/1304/1304TCTM1TW.htm |author=葉佳慧|language=zh |title=林殿威無伴奏的製琴之路 |publisher=http://www.taiwanfun.com/ |work=吃喝玩樂大台中雜誌!  |date=2013-04|accessdate=2014-03-06}}</ref>.
